posting_body: ['MUST HAVE STRONG CREDIT!', 'NO EVICTIONS!', 'NO CRIMINAL RECORDS!', 'NO EXCEPTIONS!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!', 'CALL NOW!!!!!', 'PLEASE FIND THE EXACT PROPERTY ADDRESS 1/4 INCH UNDER THE MAP IN THE LISTING FOR YOUR REFERENCE!!!!!!', 'Email Me, Call Me, or Text!!!!', 'Shawn Kaminsky', 'show contact info', 'The ultimate Florida home, and backyard!', 'This updated single family no HOA home is available for immediate annual rental.', 'Large oversized circle driveway with plenty of room for multiple cars, boat or RV, also has 1 car garage.', 'There are 3 large split floorplan bedrooms, and 2 full bathrooms, one is a cabana bath with easy access to the pool.', 'Master bedroom features an updated on suite with double vanity sinks.', 'Plenty of storage inside including a large laundry room with a new washer and dryer.', 'Fully updated kitchen, and new appliances, with a great pass through window to the spacious screened patio, and a separate dining room.', 'The best part about this home is the gorgeous backyard!', 'It is fully fenced with gates on both side yards.', 'Plenty of grass for your pets to enjoy.', 'A raised stone patio, updated stone pool deck, and a beautiful large heated pool, and spa.', 'No storm protection needed if there is a hurricane the entire house has impact windows.', 'Rent includes pool service, landscaping, pest control, and x2/year AC maintenance.', 'Renters insurance is required.']
